message:
Better handling of app lifecycle.

- Move database-dependent code from onCreate* on activities and fragments to a onDatabaseReady event.
- Added functionality for a complete clean application exit from any activity.

title: Fix validation on edit and cascading of deletes after edits.
message:
Fix validation on edit and cascading of deletes after edits.

Turns out that SQLite applies the CASCADE DELETE clauses on INSERT OR REPLACE
queries. Removed the insertWithOnConflict with pre-check of existence in the
database or not (by checking if there's a known id).

title: Fix date selection on month wraparound and remove trans no longer on period.
message:
Fix date selection on month wraparound and remove trans no longer on period.

That's what you get for not reading the documentation carefully. roll() doesn't
change higher fields so when subtracting a day to the 1st of March, one'd get
31th March. Replaced roll() with add() for correct behaviour.
